{"tid":2441974,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都好憎放假/放工要出街，好想放工想即返屋企","createTime":"2021-03-11T05:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T11:43:59.000Z","uid":40945,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"955daaf9e6a2455485eaa230defef163d06625a1","tid":2441974,"uid":40945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"朋友約食飯，都唔會想去，只係想返屋企抖。<br />\n<br />\n平時會一日平日加星期六會用黎同男朋友出街，同佢出街就好開心，唔怕攰。<br />\n<br />\n但如果朋友聚會/要一家人拜山/出街同屋企人食生日飯/陪屋企人睇醫生，而要我星期日去出街，我會極度唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n唔想僅餘嘅星期日，都唔可以留係屋企抖下。好憎出街。<br />\n<br />\n今個星期日就係要陪屋企人睇醫生，所以星期一特登拎左假。<br />\n點知星期一都要出一出街去食飯，崩潰....."},{"pid":"154692090f67e536c0509d01128f7ae13865cb04","tid":2441974,"uid":40945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"點解要玩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係好需要一日成日留係屋企叉電！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"a1de3f8b79f64cbb06119c0634a375f7a239baf7","tid":2441974,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:23:09.000Z","msg":"淨係想返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c607addf79310c6e3ba9500e8367640f8ad015f","tid":2441974,"uid":40945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1de3f8b79f64cbb06119c0634a375f7a239baf7","tid":2441974,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:23:09.000Z","msg":"淨係想返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393a6b92027dcfd98ca70e8d5e7ee16bf5cd0762","tid":2441974,"uid":283908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:37:21.000Z","msg":"唔得喎"},{"pid":"4bf255b1ca86bdd09f9421b454233adb1ba64e76","tid":2441974,"uid":40945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:41:59.000Z","msg":"點可以令自己舒服